<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Selamat Datang - Arsip Surat Digital Enterprise</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a56db; --secondary: #64748b; --dark: #1f2937;
            --light: #f9fafb; --lighter: #ffffff; --border: #e5e7eb;
            --font-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: var(--font-sans); background: var(--light); }
        
        .welcome-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a56db 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: white; padding: 80px 20px; text-align: center;
        }
        .welcome-icon { font-size: 80px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .welcome-title { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .welcome-subtitle { font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.9; }
        
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        
        .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .feature-card {
            background: var(--lighter); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .feature-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .feature-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .feature-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--secondary); line-height: 1.5; }
        
        .cta-section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            padding: 16px 32px; background: var(--primary); color: white;
            border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px; transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: #1e40af; transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(26,86,219,0.3); }
        
        .steps { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .step { text-align: center; max-width: 200px; }
        .step-num { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: var(--primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 auto 10px; }
        .step-title { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .step-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--secondary); }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .welcome-title { font-size: 28px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="welcome-header">
        <div class="welcome-icon">🎉</div>
        <h1 class="welcome-title">Selamat Datang!</h1>
        <p class="welcome-subtitle">Akun Anda telah berhasil dibuat. Mari mulai menggunakan sistem.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📥</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Kelola Surat Masuk</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Catat dan kelola semua surat masuk dengan nomor agenda otomatis</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📤</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Buat Surat Keluar</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Buat surat keluar dengan template dan tracking pengiriman</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Disposisi Digital</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Berikan dan tindak lanjuti disposisi secara digital</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Laporan Otomatis</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Generate laporan dalam format PDF dan Excel</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px;">4 Langkah Memulai</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <div class="step-title">Login</div>
                <div class="step-desc">Masuk dengan akun Anda</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <div class="step-title">Input Surat</div>
                <div class="step-desc">Catat surat masuk pertama</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <div class="step-title">Disposisi</div>
                <div class="step-desc">Berikan disposisi surat</div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">4</div>
                <div class="step-title">Laporan</div>
                <div class="step-desc">Generate laporan berkala</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cta-section">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn">🚀 Mulai Menggunakan →</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
